metadata.name: Blank
metadata.description:
“Blank” is a monochrome digital sculpture based on her childhood and a symbol of acceptance towards her introversion and negative emotions. 

Growing up with a mixed background and being exposed to different cultures, rediscovering her identity is a constant theme in her artwork.  

“Blank” has been exhibited in Art Dubai and featured in Harper’s Bazaar and the Mayfair Times in 2021.
